            <title><![CDATA[湖北十堰发生燃气爆炸事故 菜场被炸毁]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/cdscwdwef.jpg?uRYB0Oy1SMNWWn6lDi3ROm0FjvASRdGc&itok=74zeyo27" alt data-caption="湖北十堰市张湾区艳湖小区今天早晨6点30左右发生天然气爆炸。（中国央视新闻客户端）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/cdscwdwef.jpg?uRYB0Oy1SMNWWn6lDi3ROm0FjvASRdGc&itok=74zeyo27" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>湖北十堰市张湾区艳湖小区今天早晨6点30左右发生天然气爆炸。（中国央视新闻客户端）</p></figcaption>
  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/ccdwss.jpg?yVKClA6DXBtDURMsUoT2TZNtZnC3UMAR&itok=psCYROaO" alt data-caption="今早发生的燃气爆炸将十堰市41厂菜市场炸毁。（中国央视新闻客户端）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-06/ccdwss.jpg?yVKClA6DXBtDURMsUoT2TZNtZnC3UMAR&itok=psCYROaO" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p>今早发生的燃气爆炸将十堰市41厂菜市场炸毁。（中国央视新闻客户端）</p></figcaption>
  </div>
  <div class="figure-media-gallery-nav"></div>
</div>
            

<p>湖北十堰市张湾区艳湖小区今天早晨6点30左右发生天然气爆炸，造成多人受困。41厂菜市场被炸毁。</p>
<p>据极目新闻报道，知情人介绍，事发地是一个比较大的菜市场，事发时，市场已经开市营业，买卖蔬菜、吃早餐的人员很多。</p>
<p>目前，十堰市调集所有消防救援人员正在紧急抢救伤员，十堰市各大医院也正在对伤员进行积极救治。人员伤亡情况当地正在统计中。<br>
 </p>
